19s primary gateway for international travel, and Lauriston Airport (CRU), which serves the island of Carriacou. Both airports play a vital role in national connectivity, economic development, and regional integration.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"Mission\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"Vision\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"Objectives\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"To provide safe, secure, efficient ad profitable world class airport facilities and services, consistent with international standards through a highly skilled and committed workforce in support of the economic development of Grenada.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"\\u201CTo provide safe, secure, efficient ad profitable world class airport facilities and services, consistent with international standards through a highly skilled and committed workforce in support of the economic development of Grenada\\u201D.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"To provide adequate capacity for the aircraft and their passengers, air cargo and vehicle movements in a safe environment\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"To provide for and facilitate passengers, operators and staff convenience\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"To ensure continued financial viability\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"To ensure that physical development plans are flexible allowing for future expansion\"}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"Years Serving 0 + Airlines Serving 0 + Employees 0 + Passengers Annually 0 +\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{children:\"Our Mandate\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"The GAA is committed to the advancement of Grenada\\u2019s aviation sector by overseeing the development, modernization, and maintenance of airport facilities. Our primary objectives include:\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"Ensuring Safety and Security\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.li,{children:\"Enhancing Efficiency\"}),`\n`,